{
  "page": "Doniphos Paenymion",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\"><img alt=\"Volantis.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e7/Volantis.svg/50px-Volantis.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e7/Volantis.svg/75px-Volantis.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e7/Volantis.svg/100px-Volantis.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Triarch</span><br />Doniphos Paenymion</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\"><img alt=\"Volantis.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e7/Volantis.svg/50px-Volantis.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e7/Volantis.svg/75px-Volantis.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e7/Volantis.svg/100px-Volantis.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Triarch_of_Volantis\" title=\"Triarch of Volantis\">Triarch of Volantis</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Elephants_(Volantis)\" title=\"Elephants (Volantis)\">Elephants</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Race</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Valyria\" title=\"Valyria\">Valyrian</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantene</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Doniphos Paenymion</b> is one of the current ruling <a href=\"/index.php/Triarchs\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Triarchs\">triarchs</a> of the Free City of <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantis</a>. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Doniphos_Paenymion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Doniphos_Paenymion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Doniphos, like the other two triarchs, is up for re-election and many believe he is unlikely to be re-elected. Doniphos is one of the few who does not wish war between <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantis</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a>, Queen of <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>. According to <a href=\"/index.php/Qavo_Nogarys\" title=\"Qavo Nogarys\">Qavo Nogarys</a>, Doniphos will not be returned as triarch as the city of Volantis thirsts for war.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Possible candidates for his replacement are <a href=\"/index.php/Alios_Qhaedar\" title=\"Alios Qhaedar\">Alios Qhaedar</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Parquello_Vaelaros\" title=\"Parquello Vaelaros\">Parquello Vaelaros</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Belicho_Staegone\" title=\"Belicho Staegone\">Belicho Staegone</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Doniphos_Paenymion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_22\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 22\">Chapter 22</a>, Tyrion VI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_27\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 27\">Chapter 27</a>, Tyrion VII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403163044\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.070 secon